---
import { YouTube } from "@astro-community/astro-embed-youtube";
---

<section>
	<div
		class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 pt-24"
	>
		<div>
			<div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<p
					class="text-black font-extrabold lg:text-5xl text-4xl tracking-tight"
				>
					Painlessly quit porn immediately, without willpower or any sense of
					deprivation or sacrifice
				</p>
				<p class="text-slate-500 lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mt-4 mx-auto text-base">
					Putting together a directory website was a challenge. Superstash lets
					you focus on the content and makes the entire process effortless.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mt-10 flex-col sm:flex-row">
				<a
					class="items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-xl focus-visible:outline-black focus:outline-none inline-flex bg-black border-2 border-black duration-200 focus-visible:ring-black hover:bg-transparent hover:border-black hover:text-black lg:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-center text-white w-full"
					href="#"
					>Read more
				</a>
				<a
					class="items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-xl focus-visible:outline-black focus:outline-none inline-flex duration-200 text-black lg:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-center text-black/80 w-full"
					href="#">What's is this &nbsp; &rarr;</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="relative w-full mx-auto max-w-7xl items-center py-12 pb-12">
			<YouTube
				class="mx-auto rounded-md"
				id="ZktxO6adTnI"
				poster="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZktxO6adTnI/maxresdefault.jpg"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
